             was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-17-off106" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-17-off106" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-17-off106" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831210-17-cd107" type="crimeDate">4th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-17-off106 t17831210-17-cd107"></join> last, one copper tar kettle, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-17-victim296" type="victimName">
                           Griffith 
                           Hoare
                        <interp inst="t17831210-17-victim296" type="surname" value="Hoare"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17831210-17-victim296" type="given" value="Griffith"></interp>
